  "title": "C&S RESIDENT TECHNICAL OFFICER",
  "description": "<p>Supervision and coordination of the construction of the civil and structural works of the project and exercise all reasonable skill, care and diligence in the discharge of the contract period.</p>\n<p>To carry out site supervision and inspection of the works to ensure that the works are constructed to required quality and accuracy.</p>\n<p>To maintain proper and update daily records of all works done, including records of tests, inspections, status of works, safety, site diary, materials and equipment on site.</p>\n<p>To verify reports and claims submitted by the contractors.</p>\n<p>To record all variations as instructed or approved by Consultant Team.</p>\n<p>To attend to contractor’s queries and co-ordinate works of main contractor and direct contractors.</p>\n<p>Responsible to the consultants who will have overall control of the site supervisory staff and also discharge of duties are listed following items of works.</p>",
